[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.528,
    "text": "What animal are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.528,
    "endTime": 4.48,
    "text": "I'm a lizard kinda thing, I'm an iguana."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.28,
    "endTime": 9.779,
    "text": "You are one weird iguana."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.79,
    "endTime": 15.149,
    "text": "Hi, my name's Crystal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.15,
    "endTime": 15.99,
    "text": "What's your name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.99,
    "endTime": 17.34,
    "text": "My name is Vicki."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.34,
    "endTime": 20.14,
    "text": "I really like your outfit, what is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.14,
    "endTime": 21.84,
    "text": "It's like a little stage, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.84,
    "endTime": 22.673,
    "text": "Mm hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.673,
    "endTime": 24.959,
    "text": "Do you have any guesses of what I do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.96,
    "endTime": 29.330000000000002,
    "text": "Looking at the box and that, I was thinking a ventriloquist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.33,
    "endTime": 30.162,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.163,
    "endTime": 31.38,
    "text": "How do you know about ventriloquism?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.38,
    "endTime": 35.36,
    "text": "Well I watched America Got Talent, and I'm actually practicing it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.36,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 36.4,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.4,
    "endTime": 38.698,
    "text": "Do you have a figure that you use?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.698,
    "endTime": 39.942,
    "text": "Uh huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.72,
    "endTime": 42.553,
    "text": "So good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.553,
    "endTime": 44.559,
    "text": "What's in that box?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.56,
    "endTime": 48.400000000000006,
    "text": "You know what, this is my very first dummy ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.4,
    "endTime": 49.393,
    "text": "Well, hello there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.393,
    "endTime": 50.778,
    "text": "How are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.71,
    "endTime": 55.13,
    "text": "How does the puppet work?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.13,
    "endTime": 56.67,
    "text": "He's got this right here, this hole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.67,
    "endTime": 58.67,
    "text": "My thumb goes right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.67,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "- To make him open his mouth?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.54,
    "text": "Uh huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.54,
    "endTime": 62.373,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.8,
    "endTime": 66.28,
    "text": "Did you bring any other puppets?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.28,
    "endTime": 67.113,
    "text": "I sure did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.113,
    "endTime": 67.98,
    "text": "Did you want to meet 'em?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.98,
    "endTime": 68.813,
    "text": "Yes, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.813,
    "endTime": 71.644,
    "text": "Open your eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.644,
    "endTime": 72.60000000000001,
    "text": "Aww!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.6,
    "endTime": 75.612,
    "text": "Hello."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.612,
    "endTime": 76.39999999999999,
    "text": "Hello!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.4,
    "endTime": 79.60000000000001,
    "text": "Can you tell me some tips for talking with my mouth shut?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.6,
    "endTime": 82.16,
    "text": "Bite down on the back of your teeth, like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.16,
    "endTime": 84.523,
    "text": "And then close your mouth like this a little bit, right there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.523,
    "endTime": 88.35,
    "text": "And then the easy thing to do is find a voice like, hello!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.35,
    "endTime": 89.559,
    "text": "Hello!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.56,
    "endTime": 90.88,
    "text": "How you doin'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.88,
    "endTime": 95.81299999999999,
    "text": "Crystal, will you look over here and try?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.813,
    "endTime": 98.45,
    "text": "How did you know you wanted to be a ventriloquist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.45,
    "endTime": 99.7,
    "text": "It fell on my lap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.7,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "I didn't start until I was 30 years old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 102.833,
    "text": "And look at you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.833,
    "endTime": 103.2,
    "text": "How old are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.2,
    "endTime": 103.5,
    "text": "Nine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.5,
    "endTime": 105.332,
    "text": "You already know what you wanna do, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.332,
    "endTime": 106.169,
    "text": "Mm hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.17,
    "endTime": 107.12,
    "text": "That's excellent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.12,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "Do you want to be a professional ventriloquist?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.0,
    "endTime": 111.2,
    "text": "You betcha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.2,
    "endTime": 113.289,
    "text": "Does your hand or mouth ever get tired?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.29,
    "endTime": 116.80000000000001,
    "text": "My mouth doesn't get tired, but my hand gets tired sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 118.91,
    "text": "Does the puppet ever get tired?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.91,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "No, I never do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.01,
    "endTime": 123.7,
    "text": "Really, then why are you sitting on a pillow and not jumping?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.7,
    "endTime": 125.51,
    "text": "Because I'm the queen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.51,
    "endTime": 127.38000000000001,
    "text": "Where's your crown?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.38,
    "endTime": 130.22899999999998,
    "text": "It's getting polished, ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.229,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "How often do you practice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 132.9,
    "text": "Every week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.9,
    "endTime": 134.453,
    "text": "I practice every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.49,
    "endTime": 137.79000000000002,
    "text": "Well, you should, and you're amazing for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.18,
    "endTime": 140.013,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.013,
    "endTime": 141.27,
    "text": "You wanna meet some more?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.27,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 142.937,
    "text": "How you doin' Crystal?"
  },
