    "text": "That's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.173,
    "endTime": 170.5,
    "text": "- Practice in front of a mirror so that you make sure... - I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.5,
    "endTime": 172.62,
    "text": "Yep, so see, you're doing everything right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.62,
